parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag recall to provide timely repairs and replacements can lead to a heightened risk of injury or death in the event of an accident, as the airbags may not deploy properly or at all.
symptoms: No symptoms are reported
as the issue is related to the recall and repair process rather than a malfunction of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty airbag harness wiring can cause the airbags to malfunction or not deploy in the event of an accident, leading to a heightened risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag light may come on
and the airbags may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to a heightened risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbags did not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly without warning
even when the accelerator pedal is not pressed. The vehicle may surge forward
and the brakes may not respond as expected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The accelerator pedal issues can cause unintended acceleration, loss of vehicle control, and accidents.
symptoms: The accelerator pedal may stick or get stuck
causing the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly. The pedal may also be shortened or modified during repair
leading to discomfort or difficulty driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake failure can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The brakes may not respond as expected
or the vehicle may not stop even when the brake pedal is pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electrical system can cause unintended opening of windows and sunroof, security system false alarms, and potential accidents due to distraction or loss of control.
symptoms: Windows and sunroof open by themselves
security system goes off by itself
electrical problems with computers.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fire hazard can cause injury or damage to the vehicle and its occupants.
symptoms: Flames coming from the front driver's side door
burns to the driver.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Safety Concerns with Accelerator Override System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The accelerator override system can cause loss of power steering and power braking, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Concerns about the safety of the accelerator override system
potential loss of power steering and power braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Push Switch Starter Button Safety Concerns
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The push switch starter button can make it difficult to turn off the engine in an emergency, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Concerns about the safety of the push switch starter button
difficulty turning off the engine in an emergency.
